WEBVTT

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:04.701
Welcome to Cascade of Effects.

00:00:04.701 --> 00:00:16.203
These are stories about failures people think they already understand: Challenger, Therac-25, Hyatt Regency, Semmelweis, Tacoma Narrows, Piltdown Man, 737 MAX, and Titanic.

00:00:16.203 --> 00:00:26.706
Each episode follows the same question: what changed, who missed it, and how did the system turn that blindness into consequence?

00:00:26.706 --> 00:00:30.707
The pattern is never a single bad decision.

00:00:30.707 --> 00:00:37.209
It is a chain of assumptions that stays respectable after reality has moved.

00:00:37.209 --> 00:00:42.710
The headline is only the doorway. The mechanism is the story.
